parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Fluid Leaks and Master Cylinder Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake fluid leaks can cause the brakes to fail, leading to accidents or loss of control, and master cylinder failure can result in a complete loss of braking ability.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal sticks to the floor
brake fluid leaks from the master cylinder
brake pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: ABS system failure can cause the brakes to lock up, leading to loss of control or accidents.
